Class GerberFileParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • gerberFileReader.GerberFileParser
  • public class GerberFileParser

    A class to parse Gerber text files into Java objects suitable for further processing. Separate methods are provided to parse the entire file as well as the file header only. Methods are also available for parsing the file on a background thread and can notify the caller of success or failure via call-backs.
